const functions = (props) => ({
  one: props.one,
  two: props.two,
  three: props.three,
  four: props.four,
  five: props.five,
  six: props.six,
  seven: props.seven,
  eight: props.eight,
  nine: props.nine,
  zero: props.zero,

  ac: props.ac,
  eval: props.eval,
  plus: props.plus,
  multiply: props.multiply,
  del: props.del,
  minus: props.minus,
  point: props.point,
  persent: props.persent,
  plusMinus: props.plusMinus,
})

export default functions
